title: Naruto Shippuden Movie 4 / OVA 7 [1080p][DD5.1][Hi10p][Dual-Audi
description:
I'm doing 10-bit from now on. I switched from Handbrake to MediaCoder. I have been busy trying to get it working the way I want (I am finding it very buggy, also missing some features in Handbrake that made my job easier). I have a queue built up now. Expect frequent releases for a bit as soon as they finish encoding.

OVA has a higher bit rate because the source was higher quality, I used the same CRF for both.
